Support
--------------------
Installing the Monaco font
  Windows:
    Right click support/fonts/Monaco.ttf -> Install
  Linux:
    $ sudo mkdir /usr/share/fonts/truetype/monaco
    $ sudo cp support/fonts/Monaco_Linux.ttf /usr/share/fonts/truetype/monaco/
